The number \(2026\) lies on the square‑spiral whose centre is \(1\) and the numbers increase as  

\[
\ldots 5\;4\;3\\
\ldots 6\;1\;2\\
\ldots 7\;8\;9
\]

---

### 1.  Coordinates of \(2026\)

For a point \((x , y)\) let  

\[
k=\max(|x|,|y|),\qquad m=(2k+1)^2 .
\]

\(m\) is the value at the corner \((k,-k)\).  
For the bottom side (\(y=-k\)) \(n=m-(k-x)\)  
For the left side \(n=m-\bigl(2k+(y+k)\bigr)\)  
For the top side \(n=m-\bigl(4k+(x+k)\bigr)\)  
For the right side \(n=m-\bigl(6k+(k-y)\bigr)\).

The square root of \(2026\) is a little larger than \(45\) \((45^{2}=2025)\), therefore  

\[
k=\Bigl\lceil\frac{\sqrt{2026}-1}{2}\Bigr\rceil =23 .
\]

Hence the outermost ring that contains \(2026\) is \(k=23\), whose maximal element is  

\[
m=(2\cdot 23+1)^2 =47^{2}=2209 .
\]

The offset from the maximal element is  

\[
d=m-2026 = 2209-2026 = 183 .
\]

Since \(2k=46\) and \(6k=138\), the offset \(183\) lies in the **right side** (\(6k<d\le8k-1\)), so \(2026\) is on the right side with coordinates  

\[
(x,y)=(k,\;k-d+6k)=(23,\,-22).
\]

Thus \(2026\) is at \((23,-22)\).

---

### 2.  The eight neighbours

| neighbour | coordinates | ring \(k\) | value |
|-----------|-------------|------------|------|
| \((22,-23)\) | bottom side, \(k=23\) | \(2209-(23-22)=2208\) |
| \((23,-23)\) | bottom‑right corner | \(2209\) |
| \((24,-23)\) | right side, \(k=24\) | \(2401-(6\cdot24+24-(-23)) =2210\) |
| \((22,-22)\) | bottom side, \(k=22\) | \(2025\) |
| \((24,-22)\) | right side, \(k=24\) | \(2401-(6\cdot24+24-(-22)) =2211\) |
| \((22,-21)\) | right side of ring \(k=22\) | \(2025-(6\cdot22+22-(-21)) =1850\) |
| \((23,-21)\) | right side, \(k=23\) | \(2209-(6\cdot23+23-(-21)) =2027\) |
| \((24,-21)\) | right side, \(k=24\) | \(2401-(6\cdot24+24-(-21)) =2212\) |
| \((22,-23)\) already listed (south‑west) – already 2208 |
| \((24,-23)\) – already 2210 |
| \((24,-22)\) – already 2211 |

Collecting the eight distinct neighbours (south‑west, south, south‑east, west, east, north‑west, north, north‑east) we have  

\[
\begin{aligned}
S_W &=2208,\\
S   &=2209,\\
S_E &=2210,\\
W   &=2025,\\
E   &=2211,\\
N_W &=1850,\\
N   &=2027,\\
N_E &=2212 .
\end{aligned}
\]

---

### 3.  Sum of the eight neighbours  

\[
\begin{aligned}
\text{Sum}&=2208+2209+2210+2025+2211+1850+2027+2212\\
&= 16952 .
\end{aligned}
\]

\[
\boxed{16952}
\]
